#Bitcoin's 4-year subsidy halving cycle equates to an average annual diminution of approximately 19%. Explanation:

Let x = 4th root of 2.
X = 1.189207115.
If subsidy today is M, then after t years subsidy will be M/x^t.
Avg. annual diminution is 18.9207115% or approx. 19%.
